<br>
::He then embraced her in a hug, literally giving her a shoulder to cry on::<br>
<br>
&quot;Persephone, truthfully I think Hades loved you from the moment he laid eyes on you, and he never stopped loving you. As far as Menthe goes, it may have been a momentary lapse of reason. All of us are prone to them. He may have been bitter about the six month deal...it could be any number of reasons. Hades is not one to cheat regularly, if at all. From what I know of him, that was a one time deal.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=persephoneqofu>PersephoneQofU</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 183<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(4/14/03 8:22 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=308.topic&index=12>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.aishwarya-rai.com/tradi/tash16.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> But why?</span><hr size=1> ::Persephone immediately falls into his big massive arms as she breaks down into bitter tears and listens to what he has to say. While keeping her head laid on his chest, she looks up at him::<br>
<br>
B-but if you truly love someone, you remain faithful to them right? I had more reason than him to see other gods but I chose not to. Don't tell anyone this, especially my mother.... But I know that I would much rather take my own life than than be with someone else other than Hades.. <p>*~* Persephone...Queen of the Underworld.. Faithful wife to Hades... Princess Goddess of the Spring*~*</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ixhephaestusxi>IX Hephaestus XI</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 39<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(4/14/03 6:24 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=308.topic&index=13>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Not a word...</span><hr size=1> ::Hephaestus ran his rough fingers through her hair as she continued to lie her head on his shoulder::<br>
